title: Private Ranch Cabin
posting_body: Located off of US 377, halfway between Stephenville and Granbury.
Tarleton Texas A&M University is 18 miles southwest in Stephenville; Cowboy Capitol of the World.
This is an opportunity to live on private and secure property.
The cabin is quality hand-built and artisan finished, with solid granite counter tops in kitchen and bathroom, stainless steel appliances, and fully furnished.
Studio style, meaning one large open room combining kitchen, dining, living, and sleeping areas, with additional walk-in closet and full bathroom.
Hi Speed Broadband Internet, WiFi, electricity, water, laundry room, and trash service; all included in monthly payment.
This is a unique living opportunity, in a private homesteaded environment.
We are an active law enforcement family, so all state and federal laws apply on our ranch.
First and last month's payment, and $400 security deposit.
